    <title>API接口收集</title>
    <link href="/posts/api.html"/>
    <url>/posts/api.html</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>常用API接口收集</p><div class="note note-warning">            <p>不保证一直可用，请谨慎使用！</p>          </div><h2 id="图片类">图片类<a class="anchor" href="#图片类">🍪</a></h2><p><strong>名称：<a href="https://www.loliapi.com/">Loliapi</a></strong></p><p><strong>类型：二次元</strong></p><p><strong>接口：<a href="https://www.loliapi.com/acg/">https://www.loliapi.com/acg/</a></strong></p><p><strong>示例：</strong><img src="https://vip1.loli.io/2022/05/11/ypcgevJjWVMLbP4.jpg" alt="示例"></p><hr><h2 id="文字类">文字类<a class="anchor" href="#文字类">🍪</a></h2><p><strong>名称：<a href="https://hitokoto.cn">一言</a></strong></p><p><strong>类型：随机文字</strong></p><p><strong>接口：<a href="https://v1.hitokoto.cn/">https://v1.hitokoto.cn/</a></strong></p><p><strong>示例：</strong></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;id&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">6418</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;uuid&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;4a14fd11-9e45-4935-bd16-da864c361fe9&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;hitokoto&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;无垢清净光，慧日破诸暗，能伏灾风火，普明照世间。&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;k&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;from&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;法华经&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;from_who&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;鸠摩罗什&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;creator&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;范.那内海姆&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;creator_uid&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">2913</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;reviewer&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commit_from&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;web&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;created_at&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-string">&quot;1596274765&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-attr">&quot;length&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">24</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>名称：<a href="https://www.jinrishici.com/">今日诗词</a></strong></p><p><strong>类型：随机文字</strong></p><p><strong>接口：<a href="https://v2.jinrishici.com">https://v2.jinrishici.com/</a></strong></p><div class="note note-warning">            <p>说明：由于本接口的特殊性，不支持直接调用，请根据文档进行使用</p>          </div><hr>]]></content>
    
    
